        <h1 class="fca-documents-exact-page__title">FCA Application Documents for Motor Dealers</h1>
        <p class="ccr009-hero__lead">Applying for FCA authorisation can feel overwhelming if you are unsure what information and documents will be required.</p>
        <p class="ccr009-hero__lead">Many motor dealers begin the FCA application process knowing they need authorisation to introduce customers to vehicle finance providers, but are uncertain about the supporting documents and information that may be needed.</p>
        <p class="ccr009-hero__lead">Preparing documentation in advance can make the application process more straightforward and help avoid unnecessary delays.</p>
